AI Study Assistant with Context Memory
Name: Shoaib Alam

1. Introduction

This project implements an AI-powered Study Assistant using FastAPI and Groq LLM. The system is designed to answer academic-related questions and store user conversation history for contextual responses.

2. Objective

Build a chatbot API
Implement conversational memory
Deploy to cloud
Integrate MongoDB database

3. System Architecture

User → FastAPI → Groq LLM
↓
MongoDB (Memory Storage)

4. Memory Implementation

The chatbot retrieves the last 5 messages of the same user from MongoDB and adds them to the prompt before sending it to the LLM.
This ensures contextual understanding and continuity.

5. API Endpoints
POST /chat
Generates response and stores chat in database.
GET /history/{user_id}
Returns previous chat history.

